Caitlyn Jenner dresses up bootcut jeans with slash-neck top and T-bar heels as she enjoys solo stroll after spending Christmas with the Kardashians

By Helen Turnbull For Mailonline

Published: 10:06 EST, 29 December 2015 | Updated: 14:34 EST, 29 December 2015

She's enjoyed an extraordinary year.

And Caitlyn Jenner looked reflective as she was pictured strolling around Malibu, California, on her own on Monday after celebrating Christmas with her ex-wife Kris and the Kardashian clan.

The ex-Olympian cut a smart-casual figure as she ran errands in her local area following the spectacular celebrations.

Caitlyn appeared a little downcast that the festive season was over, having been surrounded by her loved ones for the best part of last week.

As well as attending Kris' annual Christmas Eve party, she spent the morning after at her Calabasas mansion with Kourtney, Khloe, Kim, Kendall, Kylie and grandchildren - Mason, Penelope, North and latest addition Saint.

The family members shared snapshots of their Christmas-morning excitement on their various social-media profiles and a range of images showed them dressed in one of two festive-patterned onesie designs.

Snap back to realty: Her expression was glum as she grabbed coffee on her own

Talking about Kristmas with the Kardashians, Caitlyn told fans on Wednesday: 'Probably the biggest tradition I have along with the rest of the family, is Kris – for the last 30 years – her Christmas Eve party is over-the-top spectacular.

'She does such a beautiful job with decorating the house. We've had the same Santa Claus for 25 years.

'It's a great time for our family, a great time for all our close friends. It just really kicks off our holiday season perfectly, and it certainly is a lot of fun.'
